{"id": "ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 159, "displayName": {"text": "Don Blanc", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poaWQyWjRRbTV2VjFsYVdYbHlXV1JwWWpCNlZtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Don Blanc is a place where you can enjoy top-notch service, fresh meat, and side dishes. The authentic, un-Americanized Korean food is truly delicious, and the servers are incredibly friendly. In particular, the two managers, John and Chris, never forget to provide what customers need, even though they're busy, and they always have a smile on their face, making for a comfortable and enjoyable dining experience. Their delightful sense of humor always makes me happy. If I could, I'd love to visit this place often. If you're craving authentic Korean barbecue, Korean beer, and delicious Korean side dishes, this is a restaurant I highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Don Blanc is a place where you can enjoy top-notch service, fresh meat, and side dishes. The authentic, un-Americanized Korean food is truly delicious, and the servers are incredibly friendly. In particular, the two managers, John and Chris, never forget to provide what customers need, even though they're busy, and they always have a smile on their face, making for a comfortable and enjoyable dining experience. Their delightful sense of humor always makes me happy. If I could, I'd love to visit this place often. If you're craving authentic Korean barbecue, Korean beer, and delicious Korean side dishes, this is a restaurant I highly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hyonny", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103333258846377537122/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlW-PjjmerwTygNq1e7kuCPuhtegLOYwsx9lywxslSvqN8Aw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-20T01:25:13.421041668Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poaWQyWjRRbTV2VjFsYVdYbHlXV1JwWWpCNlZtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poaWQyWjRRbTV2VjFsYVdYbHlXV1JwWWpCNlZtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857d85f864df71:0xb1b95209f3545463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sM0xXVlFiR0ZQZWt3MFgxQnhXVUpxWDFGM2EzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "GOPCHANG LOVER’S PARADISE\nIf you’ve been missing your Korean Gopchang/intestines you had in SoCal, this is the spot to try! The portion is decent and flavor is there! Also love that there’s potato slices in there!\n\nTo avoid long lines, come during off hours like 3pm~ They don’t take same day reservations.\n\nOther dishes-\nCold buckwheat noodles are 9/10\nSoy sauce garlic chicken 7/10 (wish they weren’t full of fried batter clumps and wanted just wings)\nPork belly single serving 9/10\nSpicy tofu soup 8.5/10 (love the tofu in there!)\nSide dishes 8/10\n\nAtmosphere-\nVery loud and the music just adds to the noise, have to yell across the table for my friends to hear me, vise versa…. During busy hours that is.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "GOPCHANG LOVER’S PARADISE\nIf you’ve been missing your Korean Gopchang/intestines you had in SoCal, this is the spot to try! The portion is decent and flavor is there! Also love that there’s potato slices in there!\n\nTo avoid long lines, come during off hours like 3pm~ They don’t take same day reservations.\n\nOther dishes-\nCold buckwheat noodles are 9/10\nSoy sauce garlic chicken 7/10 (wish they weren’t full of fried batter clumps and wanted just wings)\nPork belly single serving 9/10\nSpicy tofu soup 8.5/10 (love the tofu in there!)\nSide dishes 8/10\n\nAtmosphere-\nVery loud and the music just adds to the noise, have to yell across the table for my friends to hear me, vise versa…. During busy hours that is.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "KD", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106345724218462725253/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1sVK1I8iWi2-NklURj2UVbEqx1tkwLpA-Vy2NVk3uN5b7lzo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-26T03:19:39.379989102Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sM0xXVlFiR0ZQZWt3MFgxQnhXVUpxWDFGM2EzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sM0xXVlFiR0ZQZWt3MFgxQnhXVUpxWDFGM2EzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857d85f864df71:0xb1b95209f3545463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMVlWZEZOa3hyYkhOd1dUUnNhbTFtYlVkYVNGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "​I recently had an incredible dining experience at DonBlac, and it’s easily one of the best KBBQ spots I’ve visited. From the moment we walked in, the ambiance was spot on—modern, welcoming, and perfect for a great meal with friends or family.\n​We decided on the Supreme Set B, and it was an absolute feast. The highlight, without a doubt, was the monster rib. It was truly on another level of delicious—tender, perfectly marbled, and packed with flavor. Every cut of meat was high quality and grilled to perfection.\n​There’s nothing quite like pairing such a savory, rich meal with a cold glass of beer. It’s the ultimate combination and exactly what a great KBBQ experience is supposed to be. If you're looking for top-tier food and a great atmosphere, DonBlac is the place to go!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "​I recently had an incredible dining experience at DonBlac, and it’s easily one of the best KBBQ spots I’ve visited. From the moment we walked in, the ambiance was spot on—modern, welcoming, and perfect for a great meal with friends or family.\n​We decided on the Supreme Set B, and it was an absolute feast. The highlight, without a doubt, was the monster rib. It was truly on another level of delicious—tender, perfectly marbled, and packed with flavor. Every cut of meat was high quality and grilled to perfection.\n​There’s nothing quite like pairing such a savory, rich meal with a cold glass of beer. It’s the ultimate combination and exactly what a great KBBQ experience is supposed to be. If you're looking for top-tier food and a great atmosphere, DonBlac is the place to go!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tony Fisher", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114377546054461468169/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyu2DS-sBvUiGTp4yGT4zQzbzXRB5IBrYJuzxHamNwcpCfB64hXw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-17T21:48:42.021287759Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMVlWZEZOa3hyYkhOd1dUUnNhbTFtYlVkYVNGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxMVlWZEZOa3hyYkhOd1dUUnNhbTFtYlVkYVNGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d85f864df71:0xb1b95209f3545463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1pqZDFNamhZVW14M2RYaENlR1ZQVjNOdVoxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The BBQ melts in your mouth. One of the best Korean meals I've had in the bay, and service that sets the standard for personal care in you enjoying your food and entire meal experience. High recommend. They handled our big group of 10, made it look easy and made us feel like family.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The BBQ melts in your mouth. One of the best Korean meals I've had in the bay, and service that sets the standard for personal care in you enjoying your food and entire meal experience. High recommend. They handled our big group of 10, made it look easy and made us feel like family.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Keri Nelson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100857903247801399915/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMjwaqk-ypV6ZXkw3-pKc7yT3920UnXi51UlE96rSbOBgfOw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-31T08:41:22.161880654Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1pqZDFNamhZVW14M2RYaENlR1ZQVjNOdVoxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Wc1pqZDFNamhZVW14M2RYaENlR1ZQVjNOdVoxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d85f864df71:0xb1b95209f3545463"}, {"name": "places/ChIJcd9k-IV9hYARY1RU8wlSubE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsYWJHeHdibk5oT0RaMU5HZENOVFZPVW1wc1NHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We got the Supreme Set A for three people a bit to much food for 3 but go figure it feeds 4-5 people. But overall food and sides were hella good kimchi sour level was great and meat well seasoned. The staff were very attentive and even cooked all the meat for us. Definitely gonna be coming back", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We got the Supreme Set A for three people a bit to much food for 3 but go figure it feeds 4-5 people. But overall food and sides were hella good kimchi sour level was great and meat well seasoned. The staff were very attentive and even cooked all the meat for us. Definitely gonna be coming back", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Andrew Uyesugi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101342842444959688486/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzccBRGYHTJ1nlv5UxoHlQIJXduZHUJob22r9zmxa2Ym5aqvVN=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"